e compilation of results from the literature on emission line\nsurveys, the evolution in the cosmic star formation rate density over 0 < z <\n1.5 is measured to be rho_dot_SFR(z) = rho_dot_SFR(0) (1+z)^{3.4+/-0.4}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Mar 2010 21:40:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
